You need to first create a document that describes:

The current situation
- The problement statement
- The cause
- How the resolution of the task can be considered a succes
- Important notes

Then in a second time, you need to create a Technical dive in document that explains the why and the how the task is going to be solved. It needs to contains 3 phases:

- Investigation
- Conception
- Validation. It should provide all the context and material needed to understand what we plan on building.

In a third time, you have to create an implementation plan file that should contain the whole plan to resolve the task.

You are going to put those file in a .jules/{task_name} folder
